{"id":1842,"date":"2025-11-12T06:51:00","date_gmt":"2025-11-12T06:51:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/?page_id=1842"},"modified":"2026-03-30T17:52:07","modified_gmt":"2026-03-30T17:52:07","slug":"training","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/training\/","title":{"rendered":"Training"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\" style=\"padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2db22277 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left\">Training Packages<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-46ac7347 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:24px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized has-custom-border\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/medium-shot-people-learning-job-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1586 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/683;border-radius:20px;width:565px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/medium-shot-people-learning-job-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/medium-shot-people-learning-job-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/medium-shot-people-learning-job-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/medium-shot-people-learning-job-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/medium-shot-people-learning-job-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/medium-shot-people-learning-job-930x620.jpg 930w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Empowering People Through AI.<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Build the AI confidence and capability your organisation needs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>From foundational literacy to strategic leadership, our tailored training helps every member of your team adopt AI with confidence, responsibility, and measurable impact.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We personalise every training package to be compliant with your institution\u2019s AI and data policy. We\u2019ll also train with the same AI tools that your staff have access to.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-212821f5 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-neve-link-color-background-color has-text-color has-background wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/book-a-call\/\" style=\"border-radius:8px;color:#ffffff\">Book a Call<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline is-style-outline--1\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-nv-site-bg-color has-neve-link-hover-color-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/contact-us\/\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">Email Us<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull ticss-b05da650 has-neve-link-color-background-color has-background\" id=\"included\" style=\"padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2db22277 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-nv-text-dark-bg-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-964325fb5ff9c5c1855e7eaaf5aae615\">All-Inclusive Training Package<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ad2f72ca wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;width:369px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer wp-container-content-8e3a3ea1\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-nv-text-dark-bg-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-2a5ac098e1e4f8a0ee8faebecc99d482\">Our all-inclusive training package gives you the opportunity to personalise your training needs &#8211; selecting which workshops your staff require, dependant on roles and experience.<br><br>All in-person\/ online workshops are supported by asynchronous courses, to help reinforce and further embed learning. Monthly &#8216;AI Cafe&#8217;s&#8217; are also included, to help learners with their application and exploration journey.&nbsp;<br><br>Throughout, we regularly update you and run a data-driven strategic roadmap session at the end to support your future developments.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px;width:369px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer wp-container-content-8e3a3ea1\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-neve-link-color-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-neve-link-color-background-color has-background\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-46ac7347 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:24px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-border-color has-background\" style=\"border-color:#e5e7eb;border-width:1px;border-radius:12px;background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized has-custom-border\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"has-border-color has-nv-site-bg-border-color wp-image-1874 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 512px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 512\/512;border-width:9px;width:86px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1.png 512w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1-150x150.png 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Free Initial Consultation<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A collaborative discussion to understand your institution&#8217;s goals and challenges and see where you are on your AI journey.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background\" style=\"background-color:#01588700;color:#01588700\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-border-color has-background\" style=\"border-color:#e5e7eb;border-width:1px;border-radius:12px;background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized has-custom-border\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"has-border-color has-nv-site-bg-border-color wp-image-1917 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 512px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 512\/512;border-width:9px;width:86px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/4.png 512w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/4-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/4-150x150.png 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">On-Demand Access to Online Courses<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On-demand access to asynchronous courses that reinforce and extend the learning from our live workshops, for up to 100 staff per package.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-border-color has-background\" style=\"border-color:#e5e7eb;border-width:1px;border-radius:12px;background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized has-custom-border\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"has-border-color has-nv-site-bg-border-color wp-image-1875 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 512px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 512\/512;border-width:9px;width:86px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/2.png 512w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/2-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/2-150x150.png 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">AI Literacy &amp; Needs Analysis<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We pinpoint knowledge gaps and confidence levels across your team(s) to ensure our training is targeted and effective.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background\" style=\"background-color:#01588700;color:#01588700\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-border-color has-background\" style=\"border-color:#e5e7eb;border-width:1px;border-radius:12px;background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized has-custom-border\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"has-border-color has-nv-site-bg-border-color wp-image-1918 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 512px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 512\/512;border-width:9px;width:86px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/5.png 512w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/5-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/5-150x150.png 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Strategic Roadmap Session<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A high-level session with your leadership to translate training insights into a clear action plan for sustaining momentum.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-border-color has-background\" style=\"border-color:#e5e7eb;border-width:1px;border-radius:12px;background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized has-custom-border\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"has-border-color has-nv-site-bg-border-color wp-image-1876 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 512px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 512\/512;border-width:9px;width:86px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/3.png 512w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/3-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/3-150x150.png 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Personalised Workshops<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Choose which of our workshops for us to personalise and deliver. Expert-led, hands-on training sessions (F2F or online) tailored to your institution.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background\" style=\"background-color:#01588700;color:#01588700\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-border-color has-background\" style=\"border-color:#e5e7eb;border-width:1px;border-radius:12px;background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized has-custom-border\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"has-border-color has-nv-site-bg-border-color wp-image-1919 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 512px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 512\/512;border-width:9px;width:86px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/6.png 512w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/6-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/6-150x150.png 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Ongoing Support for Staff and SLT<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Continuous access to resources and our &#8220;AI Cafe&#8221; drop-in sessions to keep momentum strong as AI evolves. Follow up calls with SLT.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-nv-site-bg-background-color has-background\" style=\"padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2db22277 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\" id=\"workshops\">Choose Your Workshops<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ad2f72ca wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;width:369px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer wp-container-content-8e3a3ea1\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>All packages include a three-hour long workshop, which you can choose from the list below.<br><br>We&#8217;re always keen to personalise our offering, so if you&#8217;d like additional or different workshops, or you&#8217;d like to include additional people, then please give us a call.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px;width:369px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer wp-container-content-8e3a3ea1\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-nv-site-bg-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-nv-site-bg-background-color has-background\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-right\">All-Staff Workshops<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th>Workshop<\/th><th class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Level<\/th><th class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Prerequisite<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>W1. AI Foundations &amp; Responsible Use<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Foundation<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\"><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>W2. AI for Daily Workflows (Email, Meetings, and Comms)<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Foundation<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">W1 or similar<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>W3. AI for Summarising and Analysing (Word &amp; Excel)<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Foundation<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">W1 or similar<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>W4. Building Custom AI Agents<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Intermediate<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">W2 or W3 <\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-right\">Academic Workshops<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th>Workshop<\/th><th class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Level<\/th><th class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Prerequisite<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>W5. AI for Academic Content Creation (AI Before Class)<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Intermediate<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">W1 or similar<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>W6. The AI-Enabled Classroom: Pedagogy &amp; Practice (AI During Class)<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Intermediate<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">W1 or similar<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>W7. AI for Academic Assessments (AI after Class)<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Intermediate<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">W1 or similar<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>W8. AI for Researchers<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Foundation<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\"><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-right\">Professional Services Workshops<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th>Workshop<\/th><th class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Level<\/th><th class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Prerequisite<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>W9. AI for Process Improvement<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Intermediate<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">W2 or similar<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>W10. AI for Comms and Engagement<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">Intermediate<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-right\" data-align=\"right\">W2 or similar<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-nv-site-bg-background-color has-background\" style=\"padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2db22277 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\" id=\"workshops\">Senior Leader Consulting<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ad2f72ca wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;width:369px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer wp-container-content-8e3a3ea1\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>This highly interactive and personalised consulting helps strategic leaders identify opportunities and overcome challenges that AI poses to their teams.&nbsp;<br><br>Designed entirely around your institution&#8217;s AI and Data policies, this in-person workshop is focused on supporting leaders to be able to make informed decisions when it comes to the next steps in their AI journey.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px;width:369px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer wp-container-content-8e3a3ea1\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-nv-site-bg-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-nv-site-bg-background-color has-background\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-right\">Leadership Planning Workshops<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th>Workshop<\/th><th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Level<\/th><th>Prerequisite<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>W11. The AI Leadership Briefing (3-hour)<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Strategic<\/td><td><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>W12. The AI Strategic Roadmap (Full day)<\/td><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Strategic<\/td><td>W11<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull ticss-4b6d3c37 has-neve-text-color-background-color has-background\" id=\"whyus\" style=\"padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2db22277 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-neve-link-hover-color-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-6e26749cc2222eb303dd086379ad209f\">Why choose WorkSmart-AI?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-46ac7347 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:24px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-border-color has-background\" style=\"border-color:#e5e7eb;border-width:3px;border-radius:12px;background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-thumbnail is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/mortar-board-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1925 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 150px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 150\/150;width:102px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/mortar-board-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/mortar-board-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/mortar-board.png 512w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading alignfull has-text-align-center\">Higher Ed Specialists<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We have been working with Universities for over a decade, supporting senior leaders and their staff to feel confident in making effective technological change.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Understanding the business needs, whilst appreciating people&#8217;s concerns and anxieties when it comes to new digital and AI technologies, underpins everything that we do.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-border-color has-background\" style=\"border-color:#e5e7eb;border-width:3px;border-radius:12px;background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium is-resized has-custom-border\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/data-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"has-border-color has-nv-site-bg-border-color wp-image-1926 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 300px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 300\/300;border-width:10px;width:100px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/data-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/data-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/data.png 512w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Data-Driven ROI<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We understand the importance of being able to prove ROI whenever key decisions are made. That\u2019s why everything we do is underpinned by data.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>From the initial consultation, right through to training and delivery, we use cutting-edge technology to support our approach, evidence impact and drive the returns.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-border-color has-background\" style=\"border-color:#e5e7eb;border-width:3px;border-radius:12px;background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:24px;padding-right:24px;padding-bottom:24px;padding-left:24px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" data-src=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/people-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1928 lazyload\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 300px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 300\/300;width:100px;height:auto\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/people-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/people-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/people.png 512w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Bespoke Workshops<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Evidence proves that one-off workshops don\u2019t work when it comes to enabling effective digital transformation to happen in the workplace.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>That\u2019s why we offer personalised consultancy, training and support packages &#8211; working with you to meet the specific needs of your institution and your budget.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull ticss-29fe7d51\" id=\"faq\" style=\"padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2db22277 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Frequently Asked Questions<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-46ac7347 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:24px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-b6b3eacc\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion exclusive\">\n<details open class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item\"><summary class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__title\"><div><strong>What makes WorkSmart-AI different from other AI training providers?<\/strong><\/div><\/summary><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__content\">\n<p>We focus on people-first adoption &#8211; helping staff feel confident and productive with AI and supporting leadership teams to make strategic data-driven implementation decisions.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As AI specialists within higher education, we understand the needs and challenges experienced by staff, and are here to support you in overcoming them. Rather than just demonstrating tools, our training connects AI use to real measurable outcomes, like time saved, improved productivity, and better policy alignment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We also personalise our training to adhere to individual institutions AI and data policies.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item\"><summary class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__title\"><div><strong>Who are your services designed for?<\/strong><\/div><\/summary><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__content\">\n<p>Our core audience is universities and education providers &#8211; supporting both academic and professional services staff. We also work with local councils, public sector bodies, and SMEs across the South West who want to build practical AI capability and confidence.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item\"><summary class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__title\"><div><strong>How do you personalise training for each organisation?<\/strong><\/div><\/summary><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__content\">\n<p>Every project begins with a free consultation. We then continue with a needs analysis to identify your current use of AI, challenges, and goals. From there, we design a tailored roadmap that ensures all workshops, online courses, and resources address your specific context, policies and priorities. Through regular data-monitoring, we\u2019re able to iterate training to ensure that outcomes are fully achieved.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item\"><summary class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__title\"><div><strong>What topics do you cover in training?<\/strong><\/div><\/summary><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__content\">\n<p>Our training covers a range of practical and strategic areas, including:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>AI for research and academic workflows<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>AI fundamentals and safe, ethical use<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Productivity and process improvement<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Teaching and assessment with AI<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Policy development and governance<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Environmental impact and sustainability considerations<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item\"><summary class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__title\"><div><strong>Can you deliver training in person as well as online?<\/strong><\/div><\/summary><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__content\">\n<p>Yes. We offer a mix of in-person workshops, live online webinars, and asynchronous on-demand courses. Most clients choose a blended approach so staff can learn flexibly and apply their learning right away.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item\"><summary class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__title\"><div><strong>How do you measure the impact of your training?<\/strong><\/div><\/summary><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__content\">\n<p>We track both staff engagement and tangible outcomes, such as hours saved, efficiency gains, and staff confidence. For larger partnerships, we provide dashboards and reports showing the value of AI adoption over time.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item\"><summary class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__title\"><div><strong>What\u2019s included in your programmes?<\/strong><\/div><\/summary><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__content\">\n<p>All packages include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Free initial consultation<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Staff training needs analysis<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Personalised roadmap and action plan<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Access to online learning resources<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Expert-led workshops<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pedagogical best practice guidance<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ongoing support<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Monthly online drop-in sessions<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Follow-up review and next steps<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re interested in specific tools or training that you don&#8217;t see here, please let us know &#8211; we&#8217;ll be able to work with you to ensure your priorities are covered in our training.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item\"><summary class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__title\"><div><strong>Do you offer ongoing support?<\/strong><\/div><\/summary><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__content\">\n<p>Yes. Beyond one-off training, we provide Training-as-a-Service retainers for continuous AI upskilling, policy development, and impact measurement &#8211; ensuring progress and implementation doesn\u2019t stop after the workshops.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item\"><summary class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__title\"><div><strong>How do we get started?<\/strong><\/div><\/summary><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-accordion-item__content\">\n<p>Book a free consultation to discuss your goals. We\u2019ll help you assess your organisation\u2019s AI readiness, identify the best training approach, and design a package that delivers measurable results.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/details>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-e2f91ca2\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns has-3-columns has-desktop-equal-layout has-tablet-equal-layout has-mobile-collapsedRows-layout has-vertical-unset\"><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"innerblocks-wrap\">\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-270d11fb\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-ec29bf5d\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Ready to upskill with AI?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Book a call at a time that suits you, or email us and we&#8217;ll reach out.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-24e3ea01\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\"><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-212821f5 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-neve-link-color-background-color has-text-color has-background wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/book-a-call\/\" style=\"border-radius:8px;color:#ffffff\">Book a Call<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline is-style-outline--2\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-nv-site-bg-color has-neve-link-hover-color-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/contact-us\/\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">Email Us<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ad2f72ca wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Training Packages Empowering People Through AI. Build the AI confidence and capability your organisation needs. From foundational literacy to strategic leadership, our tailored training helps every member of your team adopt AI with confidence, responsibility, and measurable impact. We personalise every training package to be compliant with your institution\u2019s AI and data policy. We\u2019ll also&hellip;&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/training\/\" rel=\"bookmark\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Training<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"neve_meta_sidebar":"default","neve_meta_container":"full-width","neve_meta_enable_content_width":"on","neve_meta_content_width":100,"neve_meta_title_alignment":"","neve_meta_author_avatar":"","neve_post_elements_order":"","neve_meta_disable_header":"","neve_meta_disable_footer":"","neve_meta_disable_title":"on","_themeisle_gutenberg_block_has_review":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1842","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1842","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1842"}],"version-history":[{"count":45,"href":"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1842\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2052,"href":"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1842\/revisions\/2052"}],"wp:attachment":[{"h